# Copy to .env.local for local dev (it's gitignored).
#
# Ably API key — enables cross-device live control (admin → fans' phones).
# Create a free app at https://ably.com → API Keys, paste the key here.
# Without it, control still works but only across tabs on ONE machine.
#
# For the deployed site, set this as a GitHub Actions secret named
# VITE_ABLY_KEY (Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions) — see
# .github/workflows/deploy.yml.
VITE_ABLY_KEY=
